data.name: sqlCommand7.CommandText
data.value: SELECT Users.userID, Users.userfName, Users.userlName, Users.userEmail, Users.userStage, CASE WHEN Users_Groups.UserID = Users.UserID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS Included, Users.userImage FROM Users LEFT OUTER JOIN Users_Groups ON Users_Groups.userID = Users.userID AND Users_Groups.GroupNum = @param

data.name: sqlCommand8.CommandText
data.value: SELECT Doors.doorNum, Doors.doorName, Doors.doorMAC, CASE WHEN Groups_Doors.DoorNum = Doors.DoorNum THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS Included FROM Doors LEFT OUTER JOIN Groups_Doors ON Groups_Doors.doorNum = Doors.doorNum AND Groups_Doors.groupNum = @Param
